cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with the reconstruction of light fields using deep learning techniques, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The proposed method involves the use of neural networks for various stages of the reconstruction process, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper also mentions the use of simulated data, which could be related to multimedia (cs.MM).
